            <h5>Getting started with simple curl</h5>
            <pre>
                <code>
                    $ curl http://soccer-api.club/

                    >{
                    >   "documentation": "https://www.lironrevah.tech/projects/soccer-api",
                    >   "msg": "Welcome to Soccer API"
                    >}
                </code>
            </pre>
            <h5>Getting Competition list</h5>
            <pre>
                <code>
                    $ curl http://soccer-api.club/competitions

                    >[
                    >  "A-League",
                    >  "Austrian-Bundesliga",
                    >  "Belgian-First-Division-A",
                    >  "Big-5-European-Leagues",
                    >  "Bulgarian-First-League",
                    >  "Bundesliga",
                    >  "Canadian-Premier-League",
