                    >  "Primera-A",
                    >  "Primera-Division",
                    >  "Serie-A",
                    >  "Super-League",
                    >  "Superliga-Argentina"
                    >]
                </code>
            </pre>
            <h5>Getting Season list</h5>
            <p>Note: Season name without the year is the current season.</p>
            <pre>
                <code>
                    Example: http://soccer-api.club/competitions_id
