            <h5>Getting season data</h5>
            <p>Note: data size may vary between 3MB - 50MB, it may take time getting the response.</p>
            <pre>
                <code>
                    Example: curl http://soccer-api.club/competitions_id/season_id
                    $ curl http://soccer-api.club/Premier-League/1992-1993

                    response keys = ['Name', 'Basic Info', 'Advance Info']

                    Name is equal to the competitions_id.
                    Basic Info is json with the next keys ['Season', 'Competition Name', '# Squads', 'Champion', 'Top Scorer']
                    Advance Info is json with the next keys ['Fixtures', 'Nationalities']

                    Fixtures is a list of jsons of all the fixture happened in that season, with a lot of data inside of them.
                    ['Score Box', 'Register Teams', 'Events', 'Stats', 'Extra Stats', 'Dict Tables']
                    Nationalities is a list of jsons of all players nationalities with the next keys:
                    ['Rk', 'Nation', '# Players', 'Min', 'List']
                </code>
            </pre>
